Class EmployeeTester

  • java.lang.Object
    • program2.EmployeeTester

  • public class EmployeeTester
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will test the workings of the Employee class. it will do that by allowing the user to enter Employees. The blackboard assignment said that there would be a maximum of employees, I however have chosen to use an arrayList for this. I could implement a small counter that stops the entering for more than 100 employees, however with this Arraylist I save memory when you have less than 100 employees and I am allowed to enter more then 100 employees making this program scalable to enormous amounts of employees
